 say is a huge deal here in America), but really it's what you make of it, as the book in a way is so personal in the way it views its home country and the land and the people that you will probably walk away from it with a different perspective than someone who lives there. \u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e","rating":4,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/4305144?shelf=read"},"taggings":[{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"finnish","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/4305144?shelf=finnish"}}],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/138094158"},"likeCount":4,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":0,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"Contributor:kca://author/amzn1.gr.author.v1.XfXLz-yH-HLBXgxYWg_hXQ":{"id":"kca://author/amzn1.gr.author.v1.XfXLz-yH-HLBXgxYWg_hXQ","__typename":"Contributor","works":{"__typename":"ContributorWorksConnection","totalCount":11}},"User:5992093":{"id":5992093,"__typename":"User","legacyId":5992093,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1375422964i/5992093._UY200_CR50,0,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":true,"textReviewsCount":717,"viewableName":"Shawn Bird","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/5992093-shawn-bird","contributor":{"__ref":"Contributor:kca://author/amzn1.gr.author.v1.XfXLz-yH-HLBXgxYWg_hXQ"},"isFollowing":false,"isFriend":false,"followersCount":58},"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.aBPs9RWvKZvwVtKqPgqlMQ":{"id":"kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.aBPs9RWvKZvwVtKqPgqlMQ","__typename":"Review","book":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.nnCZQa81GyzwrM4HOsGMBA"},"creator":{"__ref":"User:5992093"},"recommendFor":null,"updatedAt":1636881350611,"createdAt":1312859621000,"spoilerStatus":false,"lastRevisionAt":1312859681000,"text":"The traditional adventures of the 